WEBVTT

00:00:00.172 --> 00:00:07.094
Dryvre brings documents, work, conversations, and AI output into one block tree.

00:00:07.753 --> 00:00:15.035
Switch the view, and the same blocks become an execution board. Nothing is copied or converted.

00:00:15.693 --> 00:00:21.932
A missing public approval keeps this task Blocked instead of letting an agent guess.

00:00:21.932 --> 00:00:28.144
When a human answers, the same task returns to To do and the loop can resume.

00:00:28.144 --> 00:00:34.649
The agent claims approved work as In progress, with its contract and context still attached.

00:00:34.649 --> 00:00:40.458
Only verified work, recorded with evidence, moves to Done.

00:00:41.289 --> 00:00:48.535
In Stream, people and AI discuss that exact block, and agent output writes back as editable children.

00:00:49.192 --> 00:00:55.234
Humans set intent. Agents close the loop.
